snippet.title: Sonic Forces Overclocked - Rising the Ranks Trailer
snippet.description:
The second of the trailers leading to the release of the project, which is projected to be released by the end of this year!

Trailer music composed by KB

Cast: 
James Dijit as Infinite
Bold King Cole as Vector
Landy as Sonic
CallMeRyan as Charmy

Art Team:
Codetrilogy 
JJsucksalot
Scallybag
Speedy_fabulous

Thumbnail logo by Vale

Be sure to check out our Twitter for further updates: 
https://twitter.com/SFOverclocked
You can also join the official discord server to talk more about the project: 
https://discord.gg/zasegM3KyQ
